{"tid":55590,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[藥劑/醫科JJ請進]食錯左粒抗抑鬱藥","createTime":"2016-12-26T13:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T14:04:30.000Z","uid":68085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78b9f01ad42e1d19793852d1ebd60e0a43bf0fb8","tid":55590,"uid":68085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"如題 會唔會有咩問題發生 <br />\n食左1日到目前為止都未有咩事<br />\n有d不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2688a1ff385225163d23f13d8a5680ca26541238","tid":55590,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:50:32.000Z","msg":"點樣可以食錯 不過我估唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf31fbedc9a1cb054389101dd152906d0376c3d","tid":55590,"uid":33322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:54:27.000Z","msg":"如果巴打本身無病既話<br />\n一粒半粒無乜問題，上網查番隻藥既side effect<br />\n有d可以會令到個人&quot;牛牛豆豆&quot;,有d會失眠<br />\n等藥力過左自然無事<br />\n食完24個鐘都持續係咁就要睇醫生"},{"pid":"259599fb52de90108c05b4f9495372d13180a302","tid":55590,"uid":60829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"精神科藥咪又係藥<br />\n食左會死會身體即刻有事<br />\n班精神病人全部死哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藥效過左就無事架啦<br />\n有病果d都唔會食一粒就無事，d藥要調較一段時間藥先keep到個藥效架<br />\n食左乜咪有乜效囉其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食止痛藥咪止痛，但食精神科藥物唔會令你有精神病架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咁耐其實你食左邊隻先"},{"pid":"a18c7b97c2e8db34e3eaa7d2fb8b77668f6492f5","tid":55590,"uid":68085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"係Bor 唔記得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我食果隻叫dothiepin HCl 75mg"},{"pid":"d5373e657789438c552d2bf2ffbe92868ef13520","tid":55590,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係Bor 唔記得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我食果隻叫dothiepin HCl 75mg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得啦 TCA都唔危險得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999288b0f8122cf820b1ca6f9c2af86e9e19d22f","tid":55590,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係Bor 唔記得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我食果隻叫dothiepin HCl 75mg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得啦 TCA都唔危險得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> TCA 係antidepressant 入面最多副作用既一個class<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}